'''郭洁'''{{BD|1912年|1月16日|2015年|11月15日}}是一名中国田径运动员。

==生平==
1912年生於大連<ref name="SportsReference">{{cite web|last = Gjerde|first = Arild|author2 = Jeroen Heijmans|author3 = Bill Mallon|author4 = Hilary Evans|title = Guo Jie Biography and Olympic Results|work = Olympics|publisher = Sports Reference.com|date = July 2011|url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/gu/guo-jie-1.html|accessdate = 2011-07-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110920091829/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/gu/guo-jie-1.html|archive-date = 2011-09-20|dead-url = yes}}</ref>
